#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Recommended Steam launch environment for Radeon (RADV) + high-end Ryzen:

STEAM_RUNTIME=1 MANGOHUD=1 gamemoderun %command%

Optional extras:
- For OpenGL titles only: mesa_glthread=true STEAM_RUNTIME=1 MANGOHUD=1 gamemoderun %command%
- If a game has stutter on first run, keep shader pre-caching enabled in Steam settings.

System-level defaults are already tuned in NovaArch.
EOF
